{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081350/extras/the_game.png?t=1736086062\" />Summoner\u2019s Tale is an Action-Platformer monster collecting game in a new way!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Collect Monsters, discover their unique abilities, build your dream squad and fight your way to save the world!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>A Demo Version Is Coming Soon!!!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081350/extras/the_story.png?t=1736086062\" />A little boy Noa finds himself in a desperate situation in a big conflict with no one besides him, but as someone from the summoner\u2019s family, he won\u2019t be alone in his journey anymore, with the help of monsters Noa will seek the truth and choose between revenge and salvation which road he will take?!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081350/extras/features.png?t=1736086062\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Innovative View &amp; Game play</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play in a normal platform camera or switch to our new third-person camera that will take your eyes! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081350/extras/Change_camera.gif?t=1736086062\" />Unique Monsters Each Monster has a unique ability!, Monsters are divided into four categories Companions, Attackers, Supporters, and Enhancers</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Companions will follow and fight beside you till their energy ends.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Attackers will appear and unleash their attack then disappear</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Supporters will appear and activate their support skill then disappear</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Enhancers will give the player a new way to travel across lands or help him in fighting with mobility moves and enhancements</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081350/extras/Monster_Types.gif?t=1736086062\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Tame Monsters in different ways</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Taming monsters is refreshing like never before some monsters will ask for battle, race, specific item, or special request! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Level up &amp; Evolve</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Battle and level up your monsters then evolve into higher more powerful forms!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081350/extras/Evo_Optimized.gif?t=1736086062\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Build your dream team</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081350/extras/Dream_Team_Optimized.gif?t=1736086062\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081350/extras/follow_development.png?t=1736086062\" />Development updates are posted every 2-4 days on Twitter at @Negm_World</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081350/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736086062","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081350/page.bg.jpg?t=1736086062","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081350/capsule_231x87.jpg?